creator: martin.heider@belox.de
text:
Create a test plan and deactivate one section.
While test is executed interactive with gui, the deactivated section is omitted.
If test is started in non gui mode, the deactivated section has been run.

This was reported in bug 23803, and has been fixed in CVS, so it should be in 
the next release, due soon ...

*** This bug has been marked as a duplicate of 23803 ***
